          </p>
          <p xml:id="i-CczQbT3s7bK9w5t41d9AYn">
            Ann-
          </p>
          <p xml:id="i-6K2jNKKCUwQXy9pLywi76j">
            Kristine Johansson (s) Jarl Lander (s)
          </p>
          <p xml:id="i-CLrrZA4PBP7gPgbDRu9hLM">
            Marina Pettersson (s) Berit Högman (s)
          </p>
